<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef84149e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2427"><num value="2427">§ 2427.</num><heading> Publication</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may establish regulations for the publication of information regarding any pending application when publication is requested by the owner.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef84149f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/577/tII/s57">Pub. L. 91–577, title II, § 57</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1549">84 Stat. 1549</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/96/574/s13">Pub. L. 96–574, § 13</ref>, <date date="1980-12-22">Dec. 22, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3350">94 Stat. 3350</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
