<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idef8414a2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1980—<ref href="/us/pl/96/574">Pub. L. 96–574</ref> inserted “information regarding” after “publication of”.</p>
